TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup the target table. If the row exists, check whether it has changed. If not, allocate a surrogate key. Override SQL is necessary to rtrim fields which otherwise won't match incoming rows to the lookup columns.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: DCLkp_D_ProductDet

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT D_PRODUCTDET.PRODUCTDETID as PRODUCTDETID, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.GAMENAME) as GAMENAME, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.SUBGAMENAME) as SUBGAMENAME, D_PRODUCTDET.JACKPOTFLG as JACKPOTFLG, D_PRODUCTDET.EGMLines as EGMLines, D_PRODUCTDET.RwrdLvl as RwrdLvl, D_PRODUCTDET.EdgeTheo as EdgeTheo, D_PRODUCTDET.TblMaxBet as TblMaxBet, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.AltGamingActvyCde) as AltGamingActvyCde, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.AltSubGameCde) as AltSubGameCde, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.AltSubGameName) as AltSubGameName, D_PRODUCTDET.SctyCde as SctyCde, rtrim(D_PRODUCTDET.GameTyp) as GameTyp, D_PRODUCTDET.GAMINGPRODTYP as GAMINGPRODTYP, D_PRODUCTDET.GAMINGACTIVITYCODE as GAMINGACTIVITYCODE, D_PRODUCTDET.EGM_GAMECODE as EGM_GAMECODE, D_PRODUCTDET.EGM_DENOM as EGM_DENOM, D_PRODUCTDET.SUBGAMECODE as SUBGAMECODE, D_PRODUCTDET.TBLMINBET as TBLMINBET, D_PRODUCTDET.TBLLVL as TBLLVL, D_PRODUCTDET.SiteID as SiteID FROM D_PRODUCTDET

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: GAMINGPRODTYP = IN_GAMINGPRODTYP AND GAMINGACTIVITYCODE = IN_GAMINGACTIVITYCODE AND EGM_GAMECODE = IN_EGM_GAMECODE AND EGM_DENOM = IN_EGM_DENOM AND SUBGAMECODE = IN_SUBGAMECODE AND TBLMINBET = IN_TBLMINBET AND TblMaxBet = IN_TblMaxBet AND TBLLVL = IN_TBLLVL AND SiteID = IN_SiteID

GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT s.GamingActivityCode, s.TblMinBet,s.TblMaxBet, p.GameName, p.EdgeTheo ,s.PtyLocNum, case when p.GamingActivityCode is null then 1 else 0 end case as AlertFlg FROM (select distinct substr(a.CasinoLoc,1,2) as GamingActivityCode, a.TblMinBet,a.TblMaxBet,a.PtyLocNum from S_ProductDet_VELO a )s left outer join (select distinct b.GamingActivityCode,b.GameName, b.EdgeTheo,b.PtyLocNum from S_ProductDet_IGT b) p on ( s.GamingActivityCode=p.GamingActivityCode and s.PtyLocNum=p.PtyLocNum)
